edu.ucla.sspace.util
Class ObjectIndexer<T>

java.lang.Object
  edu.ucla.sspace.util.ObjectIndexer<T>
All Implemented Interfaces:
Indexer<T>, Serializable, Iterable<Map.Entry<T,Integer>>
public class ObjectIndexer<T>
extends Object
implements Indexer<T>, Serializable

A utility class for mapping a set of objects to unique indices based on object equality. The indices returned by this class will always being at 0.

See Also:
HashIndexer, Serialized Form
